Author: Jake Koenig
Summary: Correction: he's won 70% of the finals he's made. It's at 76 rn and I'd sell because his life time win rate against his likely semis and finals opponents are 75% and 60% respectively and the short match structure should make upsets more likely. He's on a tear though.
